  <description><![CDATA[<p>These apartments tick all of the boxes for your next Finnish break. Located in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a>, the slopes are just a snowball's throw away, so are the shops and restaurants. There's a small living area and kitchenette in each of the apartments, but the best part is that each apartment has its own private sauna - there's nothing more satisfying than returning to a toasty sauna after a day of arctic adventures.<span></span></p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>Ideally located near to the foot of the slopes, these apartments are an excellent choice for the keen skiers and snowboarders who want to be the first up the fells. Whether you are just starting out or are an expert skier, there is something to keep everyone occupied. While you are away, why not book onto one of our <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lapland-holidays/lapland-excursions">optional adventures</a>? Whizz around on a snowmobile, take a serene sleigh ride through the forests or meander through the fells - all of the excursion meet points are a short walk from your apartments The well stocked supermarket is nearby, so you can pick up everything needed to cook tasty meals from the comfort of your apartment, and if you don't feel like cooking there are plenty of restaurants to choose from.</p>
<h2>Well equipped apartments</h2>
<p>These cosy apartments have everything needed for a comfortable stay in Finland. The apartments vary in design however the wooden panelling gives them a cosy cabin like feel, and the open plan living space is complete with a kitchen-diner and lounge area - so you'll have space to relax after a day of arctic adventures. The Finnish certainly know how to keep warm in the wintertime, with each apartment having a drying cupboard for your suits and boots, plus your own private sauna. Most apartments also have a cosy living area with a fireplace too. </p>
<p>With a well equipped kitchenette, you can cook tasty meals from the comfort of your apartment, making these a great choice for groups of families and friends looking for self catered accommodation in Levi. Alternatively, take the fuss out of meal times and opt into half board. Each day you can enjoy an extensive buffet breakfast and a varied evening meal served buffet style.</p>]]></description>
