  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Pikkukarhu 6/7</strong> are both around 54m² sleeping two to four people in a second floor alpine house style building.  These split level apartments have an open plan kitchen-living room, double bed in a windowless alcove and separate toilet downstairs.  Upstairs there is a twin bedroom and bathroom with a sauna. </p>
<p><strong>Karhunvartija 1/5/6 </strong>are around 64m² sleeping two to four people. These duplex apartments have a living room, two beds in an open area, bathroom with WC and sauna downstairs. Upstairs there is a twin bedroom, kitchen and WC. </p>
<p><strong>Karhunvartija 3/4 </strong>is around 40m² sleeping two to four. This single level apartment has an open plan living room-kitchen, one twin bedroom and two single sofa beds - one being in the living room and a bathroom with sauna.</p>
<p><strong>Karhunvartija 8 </strong>is around 58m² sleeping six people. These duplex apartments have a twin bedroom without a window, kitchen and WC downstairs. Upstairs there is a living room with a fireplace, sofa bed for two, a twin bedroom without a window, sauna and WC. </p>
<p><strong>Levin Kalle A1</strong> is around 49m² sleeping three to five people.  This apartment has two twin bedrooms, and a single sofa bed in the living area. There is two showers, a separate toilet and a sauna.</p>
<p><strong>Levin Kalle A6</strong> is around 70m² sleeping three to seven people (maximum of three adults). These duplex apartments have one twin bedroom downstairs, twin beds in an alcove with sloping roof and two mattresses upstairs. There is also an lounge, kitchenette, two toilets and two showers and a sauna. </p>
<p><strong>Isokarhu 1 </strong>is around 116m² and sleep four to eight people. This ground floor apartment has four twin bedrooms. It has a bathroom with a shower and a sauna, plus a separate toilet.</p>
<p><strong>Isokarhu 2/3 </strong>are around 121m² and sleep four to eight people. These first floor duplex apartments have four twin bedrooms. The kitchen-dining and living areas are downstairs and  there are two twin bedrooms and two toilets. Upstairs there are two more twin bedrooms, a living room and another bathroom. </p>
<p>One linen set with towels is included per person per week.</p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Wi-Fi (with the exception of Levin Kalle A1)</li>
<li>Living area with fireplace </li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Drying cabinet</li>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Well equipped kitchen with oven, toaster, fridge, and dishwasher </li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities </li>
<li>Shared laundry room</li>
<li>Travel cot and highchairs are available on request. </li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
